  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc7 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 5 \u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bbe - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One-time Visa for Foreign Investors for 5 Years - Ministerial Action",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The current economic crisis can be solved by providing more opportunity to foreign tourists and investors.",
        "Also, Investment Promotion Minister Thammika Perera said that one-day foreign passport service will be started from Monday in the outer districts.",
        "The event of granting business visa for 5 years to foreigners working in Sri Lanka Board of Investment companies was held on Friday 01st at Sri Lanka Board of Investment. He said this in the speech he participated in.",
        "65 percent of Sri Lanka's total exports are from companies registered with the Sri Lanka Board of Investment.",
        "Therefore, we have decided to grant a visa period of 5 years to the owners of foreign companies in Sri Lanka and the employees who are working in them.",
        "Earlier they had to renew their visa every year. But now we are giving them visa for 5 years.",
        "Investors should realize that we as the government are thinking and acting in a new way to build the economy in the state of economic crisis that the country is facing.",
        "We have started this activity as the initial step. By making investors happy, more investors can be brought into the country.",
        "We believe that the current economic crisis can be solved by giving them more opportunities.",
        "Also, if we can bring back the tourists who came to the country in 2018, we will get 2.3 million dollars.",
        "If we all unite and take action to bring that dollar amount, we can eliminate the existing petrol, diesel and gas system in the country.",
        "Tourists don't come to a country when they see people lining the streets and lining up. So we all have to do this together.",
        "Similarly, there is a long queue at the Department of Immigration and Emigration to get a foreign passport.",
        "We have started a separate Karumapeetham there to get them a foreign passport in a one-day service for those who have the necessary documents to go to work abroad.",
        "Also we are offering one day passport collection service from Monday to Matara, Kandy. We start in Vavuniya districts. After this, people in these districts do not need to come to Colombo for the one-day service to get their passports, he said."
      ],
